9 Section 34.41. Appropriations shall not be available for
10 contractual or expenditure purposes until allotted as provided in
11 the Oklahoma State Finance Act. Appropriations made by the
12 Legislature to each state agency are hereby declared to be maximum,
13 conditional and proportionate appropriations. The purpose of this
14 section is to make appropriations payable in full in the amounts
15 named only in the event that the estimated budget resources within
