19 fully adjudicated fine revenue received in the Oklahoma Mechanical
20 Licensing Revolving Fund, Electrical Revolving Fund, Plumbing
21 Licensing Revolving Fund or Roofing Contractor Registration
22 Revolving Fund as determined pursuant to this section. Funds may be
23 transferred only from the prior fiscal year.
