14 may be invested pursuant to this section. In no circumstance shall
15 investments be made in bonds, notes, debentures or any similar
16 obligations of a foreign government that:
17 a. is identified as a state sponsor of terrorism by the
18 United States Department of State, or
19 b. any authoritarian or totalitarian government the
20 sovereign powers of which are exercised through a
21 single person or group of persons who are not elected
22 by any form of legitimate popular voting.
23 B. Investments shall be made with judgment and care, under
24 circumstances then prevailing, which persons of prudence, discretion
