14 1. Liquidity;
15 2. Diversification;
16 3. Safety of principal;
17 4. Yield;
18 5. Maturity and quality; and
19 6. Capability of investment management.
20 The State Treasurer shall place primary emphasis on safety and
21 liquidity in the investment of public funds. To the extent
22 practicable taking into account the need to use sound investment
23 judgment, the written investment policies shall include provision
24 for utilization of a system of competitive bidding in the investment
