5 for one (1) year and two members for two (2) years. Members shall
6 serve until their successors are duly appointed for a term of three
7 (3) years. Appointments shall be made by and take effect on July 31
8 of the year in which the appointment is made. Annually by December
9 30 the Board shall elect from its membership a chair and vice chair.
